Package: DISCERNS
Type: Package
Title: DISCovery of unannotated Exons from RNa-seq Splice junction reads
Version: 0.99.0
Author: Katharina M. Hembach
Maintainer: Katharina M. Hembach <katharina.hembach@uzh.ch>
Authors@R: person("Katharina M.", "Hembach", email = "katharina.hembach@uzh.ch", 
  role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5041-6205"))
Description: The DISCERNS package predicts novel exons from RNA-seq data
    based on the SJ.out.tab and the BAM file from STAR. The mapped 
    splice-junctions are compared with the genome annotation to discover novel 
    exons. Existing genome annotations in GTF format can be extended with 
    predicted exons.
License: GPL (>=2)
URL: https://github.com/khembach/exondiscovery
BugReports: https://github.com/khembach/exondiscovery/issues
